________________________________________________________Sorting using structure and it's usage_____________________________________________________________________________

C++ er STL e thaka sort function tar naam holo introsort . Ei sort function ti muloto 3 ta different type of sorting technique
ke eksathe kore optimize kore bananu hoise . 1) Quick Sort , 2) Heap Sort , 3) Insertion Sort .
Er basic structure ta holo :- sort( starting pointer , ending pointer , comparator function ) ;
Ekhane array er khetre array er naam ta e er starting pointer ar arr + size holo ending pointer .
Vector er khetre starting pointer holo vec.begin() and ending pointer holo vec.end() .
Generally amra sort korar shomoy kuno comparator function nije theke pass kori nah . 
*) Reverse Sort korar jonne :- 1) sort(vec.rbegin() , vec.rend())   , 2) sort ( vec.begin() , vec.end() , greater<int>() ) ;

Ekhon amader kaaj holo greater<int>() comparator ta ke nijera banabo . Greater int er kaaj holo duita compare kore boro ta ke age boshanu ;
bool cmp( int &x , int &y ){
    return x > y ; // Ekhane amra ja chai thik tai return korte hobe . Amra cacchi je array te jeita age thakbe sheita jeno boro hoy .
}
*) Ekhane muloto amra nijeder ke ekta question korbo , er vitti te cmp function ta toiri korbo . Question ta holo x jodi y er cheye boro
hoy tahole ki array teh x er age thaka uchit ? Jodi amader answer yes hoy tahole return true . Else return false .

Pair er jonne custom comparator toiri korar niyom ;

bool comparator(pair<int,int> &p1 , pair<int,int> p2){
    if ( p1.first != p2.first() ) p1.first > p2.first ;
    else p2.second < p1.second ;
}

Jodi pair naam e kuno kichu c++ e exist na korto tahole amra struct er sahajje pair define kortam .

struct kromojur{
    ll prothom ; ll ditiyo ;
}
Ekhon pair<ll,ll> p1 ; je kotha , kromojur k1 eki kotha .
p1.first = k1.prothom ; p1.second = k1.ditiyo ; Tarmane kromojur holo amader nijeder created pair type struture .

Structure er subidha holo kebol pair noy amra tuple emonki 4 , 5 , 6 ta element niye o deal korbe emon kichu oi toiri korte pari .
Amra input output newar jonne loop er vitore lomba line ta na likhe struct er vitore ekta void input baniye vec[i].input() korte pari .

Class e shobar seshe dekhanu hoise je koyekta element dewa ache jara bivinno inverval cover kortese . Tara shobai mile 
L to R cover kortese ki na ta bolte hobe . 
Ei question ta answer korar jonne prothome pair er first and second value duita kei ascending order e sort korte hobe . 
Ascending order e sorted obosthay traverse kore dekhbo je segment segement intersection hocche ki na ba ager pair thik
jei bindu te sesh hocche porer pair ki thik tar porer bindu theke shuru hocche ki na . jodi emon hoy tahole bujhte hobe
L to R cover kortese nahole cover kortese nah .
